<sect>Introduction.
<p>
This document describes the hardware, software and procedures needed to
encode, play, mix and stream MP3 sound files under Linux.

It covers:
<itemize> 
<item>Encoding MP3's from a live or external source
<item>Encoding MP3's from audio CD's
<item>Streaming MP3's over a network
<item>Listening to MP3's
<item>Recording MP3 streams
<item>Mixing MP3's
<item>Editing ID3 information
</itemize>

